thread.title: Karen Jensen

author: Karen Jensen
title: Karen Jensen
text: When my order arrived I was immediately impressed by the careful packaging and condition of the plants. Beautifully large root systems on the two year old elderberry plants and large leaf buds already showing. I got the four plants in the ground the next day and they are already showing proof of growth. I have no doubt that each plant will grow well and produce lots of wonderful fruit.
